parameters: \C[23][Luna]\C[0] Ah, Noah!
Noah: Luuna, I'm glad you're safe.

\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Noah, I heard that you can't move your legs anymore. Is it true
that if it stays like this, your legs will necrotize and you'll die?
Noah: Yeah...
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] That's... Noah...
Becky: Pole, are you okay?

Pole: Becky, you're late. Leaving your newlywed husband all alone like
that.
Becky: Sorry, sorry. I had a little errand to run.
Cain: Noah, Pole, you guys are weak. That's why you get injured.
Pole: Gah. Cain-san! Why is the village chief's son like you here?
Noah: Why is the village chief's son...

Cain: There's a reason. For now, I will be joining Luuna and Becky and
acting together with them.
Pole: What reason?

Cain: I can't tell you guys. It's an order from my father. There's a
lot going on.
Noah: Is that so. Cain-san, please take care of Luuna.

Cain: We're setting out on a journey. I'll come back to check on
things later. Luuna, Becky, we're heading to the next town, Bell.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Yes. Becky: Yes.
Luuna and Becky decided to head to the town of Bell.
\C[23][Luna]\C[0] Is someone there...
